ih (authentic) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u0646 \u0623\u0628\u064a \u062c\u064f\u0647\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0645\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32662,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/05\/with-this-i-commanded-you\/","url_meta":{"origin":32667,"position":1},"title":"Hadith Debates: With this I commanded you? To argue?","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 5, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Sa\u2019id al-Khudri reported: We were sitting in front of the door of the Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, and we were debating, bringing this verse and bringing this verse. The Prophet came out to us red with anger, as if a pomegranate seed had burst\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":19913,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/10\/02\/accuser-closer-to-kufr\/","url_meta":{"origin":32667,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Takfir: Accuser closer to unbelief than accused","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 2, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Hudhayfah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, I fear for you that a man will recite the Quran, until his resplendence is seen and he is a supporter of Islam. Then, he changes into whatever Allah wills for him, such that it is\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17587,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/01\/17\/umar-islam-ruined\/","url_meta":{"origin":32667,"position":3},"title":"Umar on Islam: Muslims ruined by faulty scholars, leaders, hypocrites","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 17, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ziyad ibn Hudayr reported: Umar ibn al-Khattab, may Allah be pleased with him, said to me, \"Do you know what will dismantle Islam?\" I said no. Umar said, \u201cIslam will be dismantled by the faults of scholars, the bickering of hypocrites over the Book, and the judgments of misguided leaders.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":37558,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/12\/16\/debate-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":32667,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Debates: The Prophet prohibits arguing over the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 16, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: A group was sitting by the door of the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and some of them said, \u201cDid Allah not say this?\u201d Others said, \u201cDid Allah not say this?\u201d The Prophet heard that and he came out, his face red with anger\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":11071,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/01\/06\/arguments-people-astray-argue\/","url_meta":{"origin":32667,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Arguments: People led astray by bickering","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 6, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umamah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo people are led astray after being guided but that they indulged in arguments.\u201d Then, the Prophet recited the verse, \u201cThey strike an example for you only to argue. Rather, they are a quarrelsome people.\u201d (43:58)\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32667","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=32667"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/32667\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=32667"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuam